    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a verified time capsule, preserved in a condition that rivals its original showroom debut. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat with a mirror-like clarity, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally ceramic coated to protect the factory paint. Inside, the cabin remains pristine and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and even the original floor mats look untouched. Mechanically, the car is flawless, featuring a full documented service history and a clean title. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with precision. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life spent far away from harsh weather or salt. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade example without the typical markup, this car is an unparalleled find.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
